        "subject": "LU-10938 wbc: Server side of client-parent locked mkdir",
        "message": "LU-10938 wbc: Server side of client-parent locked mkdir\n\nIn order to be able to flush WBC data we need to instruct the\nserver not to lock the parent since we already hold the lock.\nFurnish the lock information to server for verification and\nprolongation as necessary.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nChange-Id: I71d15ee3db1905f33e028ac438b9cc3e8512d8f9\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
